{"tid":561590,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老味而家太興食嘢要加一！","createTime":"2018-02-15T06:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T02:19:19.000Z","uid":37413,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ecace292e0977f1764f399015d7ace711ad95083","tid":561590,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/15/143416_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F15%2F143416_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3c8c7abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今朝食早餐收到單都打個突，問過阿姐佢話：哦，過年係咁㗎啦。<br />\n屌你問題係而家都未過年，今日先年三十！即係閒日<br />\n你話而家年初一二三搶錢都算鳩數，大家都明，估唔到太興咁無賴，早兩日落翠華大家樂嗰啲連鎖店食早餐都冇，係呢間咁仆街"},{"pid":"8486a7c2b78745e10641ba32c0ec964575804388","tid":561590,"uid":37413,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:47:26.000Z","msg":"佢仲好似店外同餐牌都冇例明嗰吓先仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30708e5f38176f4b8e18ac22c2758fb958eb1f29","tid":561590,"uid":22447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:49:35.000Z","msg":"啱啱食完lunch加埋一要74蚊，創咗食lunch新高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e7eb8c0cc60b0fe83e1ff531f7b523163cf102","tid":561590,"uid":27359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8486a7c2b78745e10641ba32c0ec964575804388","tid":561590,"uid":37413,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:47:26.000Z","msg":"佢仲好似店外同餐牌都冇例明嗰吓先仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"報海關啦"},{"pid":"16d7710b420bfbbe29b8ba3197d9266b63f51aa9","tid":561590,"uid":86673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30708e5f38176f4b8e18ac22c2758fb958eb1f29","tid":561590,"uid":22447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:49:35.000Z","msg":"啱啱食完l